			set slot 4 of {GUI::체력직업GUI::%player%} to player head with nbt "{SkullOwner:{Id:[I;-288562697,30297737,-1181982143,1917041928],Properties:{textures:[{Value:""eyJ0ZXh0dXJlcyI6eyJTS0lOIjp7InVybCI6Imh0dHA6Ly90ZXh0dXJlcy5taW5lY3JhZnQubmV0L3RleHR1cmUvMmM4ZmI2MzdkNmUxYTdiYThmYTk3ZWU5ZDI5MTVlODQzZThlYzc5MGQ4YjdiZjYwNDhiZTYyMWVlNGQ1OWZiYSJ9fX0=""}]}}}" named "{@스킬네임}체력 증가" with lore "{@스킬로어}당신은 남들보다 체력이 뛰어납니다.", "{@스킬로어}레벨*1의 추가 체력이 주어집니다.", "&8클릭시 레벨업합니다.", " " and "{@스킬로어}레벨: &f%{스킬::체력::%player%::체력증가}% / 20"
		if {_slot} is 11:
