			set slot 11 of {GUI::체력직업GUI::%player%} to player head with nbt "{SkullOwner:{Id:[I;1030262902,46157297,-1464774994,-177525832],Properties:{textures:[{Value:""eyJ0ZXh0dXJlcyI6eyJTS0lOIjp7InVybCI6Imh0dHA6Ly90ZXh0dXJlcy5taW5lY3JhZnQubmV0L3RleHR1cmUvNDY2YTVmN2JjZDNjMWMyMjVhOTM2NmVlZTZkZmFiMWNjNjZhNmJmNzM2M2ZlZDA4NzUxMmU2ZWY0N2ExZCJ9fX0=""}]}}}" named "{@스킬네임}상처엔 후시딘" with lore "{@스킬로어}이정도 상처야 침 바르면 낫지!", "{@스킬로어}스킬레벨이 높아질수록 회복속도가 늘어나고 더 빨리 배고파집니다.", "{@스킬제한}체력 증가 Lv.5 이상", "&8클릭시 레벨업합니다.", " " and "{@스킬로어}레벨: &f%{스킬::체력::%player%::상처엔후시딘}% / 3"
		if {_slot} is 13:
